hello in French!Hello! In French, "hello" is translated as "bonjour". Is there anything else you would like to know or discuss? en Espanol!Hello! ¿Cómo estás? (In Spanish: Hello! How are you?)Which language did I use last?Based on the conversation, you used French first and then Spanish. You started by greeting me in French with "hello" which is translated as "bonjour", and later you asked how to say hello in Spanish, which is "¿Cómo estás?"
